Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.21,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,ashita he tsuzuku sakamichi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:32.51,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,surechigau otona tachi wa tsubuyaku no sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:37.64,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,"ai toka yume toka risou mo wakaru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:43.81,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,me no mae no genjitsu wa sonna ni amaku nai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:50.15,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,tsumazuki nagara mo korogari nagara mo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:55.36,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,kasabuta darake no jyounetsu wo wasuretaku nai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:58.83,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,otona ni narenai bokura no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.33,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,tsuyogari wo hitotsu kiite kure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.54,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,nige mo kakure mo shinai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:07.46,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,waraitai yatsu dake warae
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:10.25,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,semete tayori nai bokura no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:12.80,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,jiyuu no me wo tsumitoranai de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:15.80,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,mizu wo ageru sono yakume wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.89,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,hataseba iindarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.21,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,On the uphill road that leads to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:32.51,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,We pass by adults who tell us this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:37.64,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,"I can understand ideals such as love and dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:43.81,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,but the real world isn't as easy as you think"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:50.15,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Even though we keep tripping and falling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:55.36,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,We have to remember these pains of growing up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:58.83,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,For all of us who can't force ourselves to do so yet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.33,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Listen to this one thing I have to say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.54,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I won't run or cower away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:07.46,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,So whoever wants to laugh at me, go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:10.25,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Since we can't be relied upon yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:12.80,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Don't take away our seed of freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:15.80,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,The task of nurturing this plant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.89,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,That's all we have to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{Intro}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Finishing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This fight ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall look forward\Nto our next encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But do not forget I could have\Nburned your book at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:09.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs55\pos(488,499)}Meru Meru Mee!\NUmagon Critical Danger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay now, Umagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be too concerned, Umagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside, Umagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you completely disregard me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:55.15,Note,,0,0,0,,His words are literally "Why do you not even go to\Nscoop/pump water for me?" (e.g. from a well),\Nit's a saying that Umagon turns into a pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You little horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Umagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a request...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to borrow your room for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Umagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't look inside\Nuntil I say it's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I will teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to move towards\Nbeing a kind ruler,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Umagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall fight by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Baou Meruga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, we defeated the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, you can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A horse cannot ride the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even buy a ticket,\Nso don't throw a tantrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I feel refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Umagon, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.32,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\frz14.92\c&H220FBB&\pos(571.2,329.6)}Potato Chips
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.32,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\frz14.92\c&H306ED4&\pos(905.6,337.6)}Cheese
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Umagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's a horse in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What book is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen this language.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this book?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What weird writing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is this horse foreign?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Umagon-chan knows how\Nto eat at a table.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Making sheep noises is no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to share my food\Nwith horses or sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I feed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.\NGive it some of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Horse, eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Umagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.14,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\fs70\pos(172.8,451.2)\c&H312397&\bord8\3c&H86F6F4&}Awful
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it won't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. It's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sniff, sniff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That Umagon, where on\Nearth is he headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:37.77,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\frz310.3\pos(726.4,272)}Delivery
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you're anxious about what kind\Nof person will be your book keeper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will be a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not sure what\Nkind of person is good?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A good person you would\Nrecognize straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The nice-looking gardener at\Nthe hay store we always visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Schneider-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This hay is really tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, this kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where his anxiety went?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Schneider-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Merumeru, let's defeat the enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I won't ask you anymore,\Nyou coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do something about that on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This book is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally met your book keeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,By any chance, do you...\Nunderstand human speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he does!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you two are hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll invite you to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of interesting things!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My job is to deliver\Npresents to poor people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You are really a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, stop that.\NYou're embarrassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, how would you like\Nto help me with my job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What would we need to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to help\Nme carry the presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great help to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be best if I could drive a car,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I try to get in one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the horn won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So because of that, your help would certainly save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you will take on this job?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! From now on we are partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Dorouma Kotarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please call me Doronma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Gash Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Schneider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is... Umagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I thought this ever\Nsince I first saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to give this horse a name,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it would definitely be Umagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! It's Umagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!! Stop it! Don't bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! We're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, my job of delivering\Npresents will become easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, you two can wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go home for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great, thanks to\Nyou two my job went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,To have reaped such a yield.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, gathered so many\Npresents, is a first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to deliver these\Nto poor people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, presents for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Doronma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all of this is thanks\Nto my fabulous partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Umagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Now let's do some more work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But we haven't loaded anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We must hurry, Umagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, ah, you guys really are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Umagon. Gash-gon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it, the scene of the robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right, inspector Shakotan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly the work of a pro, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... This technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That legendary phantom thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the work of Doronma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My technique and your swift feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This just might work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! We're going to try\Na major challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. A big job I have not\Nbeen able to do on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.59,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\frz14.97\pos(494.4,240)}Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a big house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious present is\Nhidden in this mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want to retrieve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There are all kinds of traps\Nin that mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but with that present I could\Nsave a lot of poor people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll help, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're sneaking in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there are lots of mean-looking dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch-dogs? Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do this job if\Nyou're afraid of dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I see. Okay, let's go, Umagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If we take this and feed it to the leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,any dog would... Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha! I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an unnecessary move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly, inside the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, from here on, use this scope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see the red lines, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you touch them, the alarm switch will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww! That's not fair, Umagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Grr... In that case we must\Nfinish the job at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not matter what you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who has been called\Nthe artist of thievery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a display of phantom\Nthief Doronma's skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've stepped on the spikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys just stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The safe is just in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just be of use when I run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm saying I was just pulling your leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, I need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I took far too much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, with this, the PIN code to\Nopen the safe will be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Incorrect PIN code.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}As a security measure, the\NPIN code will be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Incorrect PIN code.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}As a security measure, the\NPIN code will be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stay over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Doronma, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You must stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn, I've wasted even more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, I've got the diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You are completely surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender peacefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You are completely surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender peacefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We've set off every alarm there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's natural this has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got the "goronbingu\Ndiamond super-one"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The super-one is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All you poor people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a present now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Such... Such a needless action...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is inspector Shakotan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have arrested phantom\Nthief Doronma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The diamond is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha.. You two really were a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to take\NDoronma somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I'm really... a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sorry about deceiving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I will try hard to be\Na person who deserves your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, then what will\Nhappen to Umagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The future battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fights?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. You were able to read\NUmagon's book, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Book?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. This book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it was this page.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. A fly got squashed and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you can have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But what country is this book from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't read it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Umagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure one day a wonderful\Npartner will appear for him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need to look after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go home, Umagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother's delicious food is waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:12.62,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Stars atarashii mirai e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:17.46,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,akiramenai hitori janai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:23.88,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,mou mayowanai yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.89,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,me no mae no genjitsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:40.90,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,he kon de shimau koto hoshi no kazu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:44.78,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,yuugure no aka wo mita
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:49.78,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,boku ni hitsuyou na kawaranai yuuki
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:53.70,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,boku wa boku de kimi wa kimi no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:57.83,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,yuzurenai jounetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:04.59,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,me wo sorasazu ni tatakai tsuzukeru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.22,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,We've gotta take the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:14.68,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,sorezore no nido to nai toki wo kizamou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:18.81,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,shinjitsu wa Rhythm Nation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:25.61,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,toki no nagare ni makenaide arukou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:30.82,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:12.62,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Stars, to the new tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:17.46,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,don't give up, you are not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:23.88,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I have no more doubts, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.89,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,to the truth before my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:40.90,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,to the things I give in to, the number of stars
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:44.78,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I saw the redness of evening
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:49.78,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,the unchanging courage that I need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:53.70,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,me and mine, you and yours
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:57.83,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,unyielding passion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:04.59,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,don't turn your eyes away, continue to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.22,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,We've gotta take the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:14.68,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,try to carve the moments that won't come again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:18.81,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,truth is Rhythm Nation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:25.61,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,don't lose to the flow of time, walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:30.82,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a terrible injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago, rescue him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be meddlesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there no such thing as kindness to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw away your optimism.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Be heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think you can change\Na person by force alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Konjiki no Gash Bell:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:22:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumbling Snowfield!\NA Regal Presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All those who fight me\Nwill just understand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:23:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the foolishness of\Nmaking me their enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:04.07,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs60\bord3\pos(488,465)}Rumbling Snowfield!\NA Regal Presence

